Response to
Episode 1 - "Standing Up in the Milky Way"
@-------------------------------------------------
 - Seeing Obama was surprising, I didn't know he was involved in the production of this!

 - I remember going to the Museum of Natural History as a kid and I would always see the same exhibit every time, which was some cool demonstration about space. I've liked    the topic ever since I was a wee lil boy, and this episode gave me a nostalogic feeling :)

 - I also did not know there was an original series and this is sort of a reboot! (gosh im young)

