 - The Cosmic Calendar was really cool and I really liked the analogy he made with a regular, Gregorian calendar and how all of human history would be in the last minute of   the last day - makes me feel insignificant and significant at the same time. We are but specks in the universe, but this thought doesn't sadden me. It just makes me feel   extra happy that I'm one of the specks that happen to exist at this very time. 

