@-------------------------------------------------

 - The whole usage of astronomy and stuff reminds me of how massive structures, like the Great Pyramid, and Stonehenge, line up with certain cosmic events. Makes sense - as   primitive humans only way to measure time and stuff was via the sky, and even today it's based off the sun and stuff, just in a form that's easier for us to see (clocks    and stuff)

